title: Smoke plumes
info:
Real instruments and Synth - Pink Floyd at its best, without Pink Floyd.
The original MIDI was written in 2001. In 2006 Mark Knight decided to try and create the track he always intended in his head so approached an internet collaboration site to complete it. 18 months later, this is the result.

Download at http://www.gamesounds.co.uk/audio/showreel/rock/mk_smoke_plumes.mp3
